    <h3>Here are some clues:</h3>
    <p>Form the stem by taking off the 're' ending.</p>
    <p>Then add the correct ending to the stem for each person</p>
    <p>The endings (not in the right order) are: '', 'ez', 's', 'ons', 'ent'</p>
